<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>10.Next.js | Next-gen Tech Edu</title><link>https://ng-tech.icu/books/react-notes/10.next.js/</link><atom:link href="https://ng-tech.icu/books/react-notes/10.next.js/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><description>10.Next.js</description><generator>Wowchemy (https://wowchemy.com)</generator><language>zh</language><image><url>https://ng-tech.icu/media/sharing.png</url><title>10.Next.js</title><link>https://ng-tech.icu/books/react-notes/10.next.js/</link></image><item><title>01.创建 Next.js 应用</title><link>https://ng-tech.icu/books/react-notes/10.next.js/01.%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA-next.js-%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ng-tech.icu/books/react-notes/10.next.js/01.%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA-next.js-%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="创建-nextjs-应用">创建 Next.js 应用&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>要用 React 从头开始构建一个完整的网络应用，有许多重要的细节需要考虑：&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>代码必须使用 webpack 这样的捆绑器进行捆绑，并使用 Babel 这样的编译器进行转换。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>你需要进行生产优化，如代码拆分。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>你可能想对一些页面进行静态预渲染，以提高性能和 SEO。你可能还想使用服务器端渲染或客户端渲染。&lt;/li>
&lt;li>你可能要写一些服务器端的代码来连接你的 React 应用和你的数据存储。&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>一个框架可以解决这些问题。但这样的框架必须有正确的抽象水平&amp;ndash;否则它不会很有用。它还需要有很好的 &amp;ldquo;开发者体验&amp;rdquo;，确保你和你的团队在写代码时有一个惊人的体验。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>02.页面路由</title><link>https://ng-tech.icu/books/react-notes/10.next.js/02.%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ng-tech.icu/books/react-notes/10.next.js/02.%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1/</guid><description/></item><item><title>03.资源准备</title><link>https://ng-tech.icu/books/react-notes/10.next.js/03.%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ng-tech.icu/books/react-notes/10.next.js/03.%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87/</guid><description/></item><item><title>04.预渲染与数据抓取</title><link>https://ng-tech.icu/books/react-notes/10.next.js/04.%E9%A2%84%E6%B8%B2%E6%9F%93%E4%B8%8E%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E6%8A%93%E5%8F%96/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ng-tech.icu/books/react-notes/10.next.js/04.%E9%A2%84%E6%B8%B2%E6%9F%93%E4%B8%8E%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E6%8A%93%E5%8F%96/</guid><description/></item><item><title>05.API 路由</title><link>https://ng-tech.icu/books/react-notes/10.next.js/05.api-%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ng-tech.icu/books/react-notes/10.next.js/05.api-%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1/</guid><description/></item><item><title>06.引用部署</title><link>https://ng-tech.icu/books/react-notes/10.next.js/06.%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ng-tech.icu/books/react-notes/10.next.js/06.%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/</guid><description/></item></channel></rss>